<H2> Recent research and publications </H2>

I work in the following areas-- 

<UL> 
<LI> <B> Cryptography:</B> You can find <!WA1><a href="http://www-cse.ucsd.edu/users/mihir/papers/crypto-papers.html"> 
papers</a> and a <!WA2><a href="http://www-cse.ucsd.edu/users/mihir/crypto-res.html"> research summary</a>. <P>

<LI> <B> Complexity theory:</B> (Probabilistic proofs and approximation, 
interactive proofs, randomness.)  You can find <!WA3><a href="http://www-cse.ucsd.edu/users/mihir/papers/
complexity-papers.html"> papers and surveys</a> and a <!WA4><a
href="http://www-cse.ucsd.edu/users/mihir/complexity-res.html"> research summary</a>. <P> 

<LI> <B> Other:</B> (Computationl learning theory, distributed computing.) 
You can find <!WA5><a href="http://www-cse.ucsd.edu/users/mihir/papers/other-papers.html"> 
papers</a> and a <!WA6><a href="http://www-cse.ucsd.edu/users/mihir/other-res.html"> research summary</a>. <P> 

</UL> 

I have only listed work from 1992 onwards. If you want an earlier
paper, please contact me. <P>

